:1701064,"uid":129812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:19:47.000Z","msg":"個宿舍隔音唔好，<br />\n隔離個roommate 鼻鼾聲勁大。曾經試過有晚兩三點聽到佢條女叫床聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nShare kitchen 佢又用到個廚房勁dirty<br />\n<br />\n回想起，嗰年真係惡夢"},{"pid":"4c9dc2cdafc247a7cbf0e577dcf36d4b23645ea1","tid":1701064,"uid":149342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:21:07.000Z","msg":"咁好易搞，買coke 落媚藥就得"},{"pid":"0b5fbdcca7bf86a8c957d0c19fd440ef6b91396f","tid":1701064,"uid":300566,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T00:41:18.000Z","msg":"我唔係留學生 我係local<br />\n但喺外國嘅大學讀書<br />\n<br />\n曾經有幾個緬甸留學生室友<br />\n污糟同煮野食臭已經唔係重點<br />\n<br />\n佢喺屋企屙屎 結果屙屎屙到落地板 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n煮煮下野佢突然將我煮緊嘅野係嗰煮食爐度搬走<br />\n話要幫佢朋友煮野食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺屋企食煙（似係私煙） 同佢講佢又繼續食<br />\n搞到我哮喘咗成個幾月 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n又唔將生同熟嘅食物冚好<br />\n啲汁醬搞到成個雪櫃黐𣲷𣲷 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢被人踢走之前 佢嘅戰績就有<br />\n<br />\n爐頭壞咗兩個<br />\n門整壞咗<br />\n成日水浸 地板同櫃門霉霉爛爛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"debcfe3bd35f508fda13d406373003ab2d86da40","tid":1701064,"uid":108269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:18:37.000Z","msg":"印度人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"479cb4635fb58ed536ef51178e6802f1713b27e8","tid":1701064,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d5c69d515a3436a792c645555d58ff4e7eded974","tid":1701064,"uid":258144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T22:50:20.000Z","msg":"我用過一次嘅花生醬再打開居然就呢食完<br />\n蛋又俾佢食左 diet coke又俾佢飲左<br />\n今日先發現啲嘢食成日少咗原來係佢偷嚟用<br />\n正一大種乞兒<br />\n佢仲要用完我個煎pan唔洗<br />\n等我要用就自己洗翻<br />\n佢仲要同另一個roommate講個煎pan同野食係佢買嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T01:22:29.000Z","msg":"咩國家既人？"},{"pid":"1599331351ab0e67a40526da24062776510a23fe","tid":1701064,"uid":96169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c3dc1e426aa2495b4a94a3a16471b73652996e0","tid":1701064,"uid":258144,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T22:53:12.000Z","msg":"共狗國家可能想徹底實行共產主義<br />\n不過其實本質只係個乞衣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T00:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係因為共產國家？"},{"pid":"3252bc5fa097c4535cfcdd65e5b13eae63b746e2","tid":1701064,"uid":86643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T00:50:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19d610cf6dcffc997611e9dafe0358d51c3d27cc","tid":1701064,"uid":230662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T00:52:26.000Z","msg":"Studio萬歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係就係孤獨啲但唔使煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ccb81b4d12350f4058858f08075e63fa7b66b2","tid":1701064,"uid":154557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T00:54:00.000Z","msg":"最撚衰格嘅唔可以唔提黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde018f3ef1c3d01bdefbe3ff020ce004a39b31d","tid":1701064,"uid":96032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:01:06.000Z","msg":"我算好彩，暫時啲housemate都幾好人<br />\n係間唔中煮完嘢食洗剩個pan或者一隻碗冇洗，不過一隻半隻就算啦，算可接受<br />\n比較接受唔到嘅係，同房個德國仔手腳唔係幾乾淨<br />\n喺間屋就冇乜嘢，係偶爾R下零食咁，我又冇乜所謂，我擺出嚟原意都請大家食姐<br />\n但佢會係出面偷嘢，佢唔係直接偷，而係會換走人哋個價錢牌<br />\n例如買對鞋1000蚊，佢就會搵對300蚊嘅交換label，咁就用300蚊買到對1000蚊嘅鞋<br />\n條仆街仲要好proud of呢個行為咁周圍同人講，話起碼佢有畀錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df519c4c27fb89696a402df0694b10e4dbdc38aa","tid":1701064,"uid":57337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:04:14.000Z","msg":"試過有個大陸roomate食剩個pizza就咁扔係kitchen一個月，之後我一打開個pizza盒，入面全部都係咀蟲，一開始我仲以為係米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知望真D全部都識郁"},{"pid":"e448a03bfd981e2cd888479ae5c64cbc8e4b44b3","tid":1701064,"uid":268178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:16:05.000Z","msg":"比3個南亞人折磨過 煮完飯唔識清潔 碗碟至少放一個星期 凌晨兩點喺度煮咖喱勁大浸味 日日帶一大堆人上黎嘈到凌晨四五點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e966474f0d115ddf36182166890fa912d9e347a","tid":1701064,"uid":268540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T01:18:17.000Z","msg":"零晨時份用機榨蘋果汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n朝早沖涼個陣一定播歌<br />\n佢個鬧鐘永遠係佢入咗廁所先響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘈撚柒醒我<br />\n零晨個陣facetime係開speaker同自己好大聲<br />\n以上係同一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f471f76303e16828e08cf61d0a5e175169ed693","tid":1701064,"uid":119810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T06:28:11.000Z","msg":"乜柒都偷 <br />\n利申：紐西蘭"}]}